Regarding Chemistry: A Molecular Approach

Missing two pages have been uploaded. Mastering Chemistry watermarks printed pages now, though, so they're print screened and, thus, might have slight inconsistencies.

I'd be really happy if you could get "A Unified Approach" Vector Calculus by Hubbard. It has great reviews and I need it for my multivariable course. I'm from Uruguay and I cannot buy it! THANKS! Please!
